OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAnti-Semitism in worldwide 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsurge, Israeli report says 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of anti-Semitic incidents   
OL,6, around the world dramatically increased
OL,7, last year, a study by Tel Aviv         
OL,8, University has found.                  
OL,10,FThe report identifies the US, Canada,  
OL,11,Fthe UK, Germany and Australia as among 
OL,12,Fcountries where there was a sharp rise.
OL,14,FThis was fuelled by radical left- and  
OL,15,Fright-wing political movements and     
OL,16,Fincitement on social media, it says.   
OL,18,FThe report's release coincides with    
OL,19,FIsrael's Holocaust Remembrance Day,    
OL,20,Fwhich begins on Wednesday night.       
